  "instructions": [
    "In a large stockpot, combine beef broth, smoked paprika, ground cinnamon, ground ginger, star anise, and onion. Bring to a boil over high heat, then reduce heat to low and simmer for 1 hour.",
    "Add sliced beef brisket or chuck to the pot and simmer for an additional 30 minutes, or until tender.",
    "Remove the star anise and any excess fat from the pot. Season the broth with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Cook the rice noodles according to package instructions and drain.",
    "To assemble the Pho, place cooked noodles in a bowl and add slices of beef, followed by bean sprouts, a sprinkle of chopped mint and basil, and a squeeze of lime juice. Serve immediately and enjoy!",
    "If desired, drizzle with bean sauce and garnish with additional herbs and lime wedges."
